Fourth Department

June, 1937.

(June 30, 1937.) In the Matter of the Final Judicial Settlement of the Account of Joseph Gitsky, Executor, etc., of William H. Gitsky.

Transferred to the Appellate Division, First Department, for determination. Present — Sears, P. J., Edgcomb, Crosby, Lewis and Cunningham, JJ.
